query:
WITH expired AS (
                SELECT id
                FROM links_main
                WHERE last_seen < (CURRENT_DATE - $1::int)
                ORDER BY id
                LIMIT $2
            ),
            deleted AS (
                DELETE FROM links_main
                USING expired
                WHERE links_main.id = expired.id
                RETURNING 1
            )
            SELECT COUNT(*)::bigint AS "deleted_count!: i64"
            FROM deleted;
